Date: Sun, 12 Jul 2026 16:00:05 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] darling: complete rootless shellspawn lifecycle

Consolidate readiness retry, full-session shutdown, structured protocol failure reporting and fast-exit completion handling while keeping the readiness delay hook as a separate test-only patch.
